### 입출력 예

> | citations       | return |
> | --------------- | ------ |
> | [3, 0, 6, 1, 5] | 3      |

### 코드

```javascript
function solution(citations) {
  const arr = citations.sort((a, b) => a - b);
  let result = [];
  for (let i = 0; i < arr.length; i++) {
    result.push(Math.min(arr[i], arr.length - i));
  }
  return Math.max(...result);
}
```

